					<br /><b>Joined:</b> Sun Apr 13, 2008 11:12 am<br /><b>Posts:</b> 2349<br /><b>Location:</b> seattle
				</span>

			</td>
			<td valign="top">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The registers of the PPU are mostly not readable (Exceptions: $2002, $2004 and $2007). You'll need to keep track of the value you wrote to them, rather than being able to read the value back.</div>

					
							<br /><br />
							<span class="gensmall">Last edited by <a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=3512">lidnariq</a> on Tue Nov 12, 2013 2:05 pm, edited 1 time in total.</span>
