				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">$2000 is a write register, you cannot read the value from it. If you want to do things like that, store the value it is in RAM as well. Also, you don't need to use another register (X) like you did.<br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">lda mirror2000<br />eor #%00000010<br />sta mirror2000<br />sta $2000<br /></div></div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

